root: ^After the incident, Magnaphyte and Bitinax wanted to make their divorce final. However, they did not know what a divorce was, so they invented a divorce dinner ritual. They both met at a table by the temple and served each other a "dish" from their own realm. The dinner was so akward, the cringe resonated through every plane of existence.
^Nobody wants to talk to about this interminable night. I don't even know why I am writing about it. I am severly uncomfortable. Make it stop. Please. I am dying.
^The new Messenger was a stone and their adventure has just begun...
